      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 24.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 24.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>物或惡之，故有道者不處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Hence those who pursue (the course) of the Dao do not adopt and allow them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
